An S4 class to define the glmmSeq output

Slots

formula

The model formula

stats

the statistics from the glmm fit

predict

The predicted interception values

reducedFormula

The reduced formula with removed random effects

countdata

The input expression data

metadata

The input metadata

modelData

the model data for the glmm

optInfo

Information on whether the model was singular or converged

errors

Any errors

variables

The variables used in the formula
